      • postInit

        public abstract void postInit(java.lang.String[] optionalDependencies,
                              java.lang.Object... providedObjects)
        Adapts the module with it's optional dependencies. At the stage of initialization, the optional dependencies, as defined in this module's metadata have been initialized.
        Parameters:
        optionalDependencies - An array of all the optional dependencies that were found and initialized.
